    <p class="breadcrumbs">You are here: <a href="/en.html?id=4">Government.no</a> / <a href="/en/dep/fin.html?id=216">Ministry of Finance</a> / <a href="/en/dep/fin/The-Ministry.html?id=221">The Ministry</a> / <a href="/en/dep/fin/The-Ministry/About-the-Ministry.html?id=240">About the Ministry</a> / <a href="/en/dep/fin/The-Ministry/About-the-Ministry/Departments.html?id=243">Departments</a> / <span>Financial Markets Department</span>
</p>
